import dollarUSLocale from "../../utils/dollarUSLocale"; const TotalCashPrice = ({ pricing, requiredEquipment }) => { return (
  • ${pricing.targetPaasMonthlyPrice} /mo
  • ${pricing.annualRebateOffSeason} Annual rebate from off-season
  • Total number of batteries {requiredEquipment.totalBateries}
  • Total number of chargers {requiredEquipment.totalChargers}
  • Total Cash Price {dollarUSLocale.format(pricing.totalCashPrice)}
  • Price/mo at 36 mos. 3.99% {dollarUSLocale.format(pricing.priceMo36)}
  • Price/mo at 48 mos. 4.99% {dollarUSLocale.format(pricing.priceMo48)}
); }; export default TotalCashPrice;
